I want to think about framing the reason for our scenarios in terms of the business goals we talked about, or iterate the q deck as our thinking evolves:

Support caregivers and families through the matching process to increase success rates, trust, and satisfaction. Extend the period of meaningful interaction on the <http://Care.com|Care.com> platform to reduce early disintermediation. 

<http://Care.com|Care.com> will use the rollout period to test and evaluate success of one or more desired business outcomes:  

Increase premium account conversion rates
Improve match rates (currently difficult to measure)
Increase job posting and/or job post quality 
Positively impact NPS and WOM to help organic growth
Gain insights prior to disintermediation
